I've just released version 1.0.1 of mgmt!

> 65 files changed, 3754 insertions(+), 305 deletions(-)

This is a small release to help out some of the packaging folks.

With that, here are a few highlights from the release:

* We added a standalone "grow" command to the tools sub command.

* The exec resource has a new ifequals param. It also got a nifcmd param.

* A new gsettings resource was added. A new fwattr resource was added too!

* There's an http:server:ui set of resources that have been added. Check out:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8vz1MMGkuik for some examples of that in action
and more!

And much more...


